5</Width><Height>210</Height><Bytes>0</Bytes><Caption /><ThumbnailUrl>/RXLImages/7/NERJ-PLAhotel_Guest_Room_1_thumb.jpg</ThumbnailUrl><ThumbnailWidth>80</ThumbnailWidth><ThumbnailHeight>60</ThumbnailHeight><ThumbnailBytes>0</ThumbnailBytes><PhotoType>OtherPhotos</PhotoType></Photo><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>General</Type><Text>Boasting a wonderful location in the town of Nerja (Malaga), the Plaza Cavana Hotel is a welcoming 3 star hotel in the Costa del Sol , in Spain . It offers great value for money accommodation right across Cavana Square and in close proximity to the Balcony of Europe, a former 9th century castle converted into a stunning viewing point overlooking the Mediterranean Sea. The hotel is also near the Sierra Almijara mountain range, and is, therefore, the perfect lodging for a romantic getaway with your beloved one. The Plaza Cavana Hotel features an indoor unheated swimming pool (closed during the summer season), a heated rooftop pool ... (open all year, except rainy days or bad weather), where you can cool off comfortably, and then enjoy a delicious snack from the bar at the lounge zone. Spoil yourself rotten in the hotel's sauna and Jacuzzi. The sporty-types will love the small, whereas well-equipped gym, while walkers will be stunned by the dramatic mountain scenery of the nearby Sierra de Almijara and Sierra Tejeda mountain ranges. Enjoy the golden sandy beach only 490 feet (150 metres) away from the hotel. The extremely helpful and kind hotel staff will give you valuable tips about the most interesting points of the area. You can take advantage of the free wireless Internet access available throughout the building. For visitors attending business engagements or social events, the hotel also has 2 spacious meeting rooms, fully-equipped with modern audiovisual amenities. Moreover, the Plaza Cavana Hotel in Nerja features a garage.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>SurroundingArea</Type><Text>The Plaza Cavana Hotel is in the heart of Nerja on the Costa Del Sol, next to the famous Balcon de Europa and amongst the shopping and leisure facilities in town. The spectacular Nerja caves, which are two miles from the centre of town, are well worth a visit and you will find all major water sports including water skiing, scuba diving and sailing on the fabulous beaches in the area.</Text></Description><Amenity><Code>Safe</Code><Text>Safe</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>IndoorPool</Code><Text>Indoor swimming pool</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>OutdoorPool</Code><Text>Outdoor swimming pool</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>AirConditioning</Code><Text>Air conditioning</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>MiniBarInRoom</Code><Text>Mini-bar</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>RoomService</Code><Text>Room service</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>HairDryer</Code><Text>Hair dryer</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>MoneyExchange</Code><Text>Money exchange</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Bar</Code><Text>Bar</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>PublicInternetAccess</Code><Text>Public internet access</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>LaundryService</Code><Text>Laundry service</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>CarPark</Code><Text>Car parking</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>ReceptionArea</Code><Text>Reception Area</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>CheckIn24hr</Code><Text>24hr. CheckIn</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Reception24hr</Code><Text>24hr. Reception</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Lift</Code><Text>Lift</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>ConferenceRoom</Code><Text>Conference Room</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>TVRoom</Code><Text>TV Room</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>RestaurantNonSmokingArea</Code><Text>Restaurant - non-smoking area</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>WLANAccessPoint</Code><Text>WLAN Access Point</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>BicycleRental</Code><Text>Bicycle Rental</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>FreshWaterPool</Code><Text>Fresh Water Pool</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>HeatedPool</Code><Text>Heated Pool</Text></